reviewText: I gave this to my father for his 80th Birthday last week. The card is very nice!  My father loved it immediately when he opened, even before he even saw the DVD in the back of the card.  He called me, full of excitement, as soon as he watched the video.  He enjoyed it very, very much!  I would definitely recommend buying this item.
Sent this to a friend.  She loved it.
It's a very cool card but it is a gift  so I did not get to see the dvd yet.
